                    </a>
                    <a href="https://fun-and-fly.com/spot/bilene/">
                        <img src="/images/accueil/partners/fun-and-fly-sport-away-logo.webp" alt="Fun-and-fly Logo">
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://kitelab.info/fr/">
                        <img src="/images/accueil/partners/kitelab-logo.webp" alt="Kitelab Logo">
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
		<div id="whoweare" class="flexi">
            <figure>
                <img src="/images/accueil/7.webp" alt="welcoming team of riders" loading="lazy">
                <figcaption>
                    <h2>Who are we?</h2>
                    <p>Teresa, Pereira, Guillaume, 3 passionate individuals who wanted to share their passion for <em>board sports</em> around the world and especially in <em>Mozambique</em>. <br>
                    <a href="https://youtu.be/XeEac9lFaYk" target="_blank">Watch the video of our discovery trip</a>.</p>
                </figcaption>
            </figure>
        </div>
		</main>
